{"tid":1365662,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【老鼠安二號】性上癮張致痕瞞女友 與女粉絲誕下兒子 宣布結婚 女友上IG才知道","createTime":"2019-07-25T16:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T12:13:33.000Z","uid":242050,"like":1,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"d0dec193a2e36c2710178b8c79e5c40e6faa22c4","tid":1365662,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:59:22.000Z","msg":"取代老鼠安紅館檔期的BOYZ成員張致痕今日在Instagram揭曉婚訊，更發布與女粉絲雯雯已育有一兒。正當所有網民及朋友恭喜他們、叫佢生生性性之際，剛剛夜晚被現任女友April大爆原來佢哋仍未分手，今日想IG先知道原來佢已經一早生左仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要同另一個女人結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢仲係Steven IG留言大爆Steven爭佢好多錢，有好多野都係女方屋企，仲話前幾日先話完好愛對方。叫Steven醫院見！（好驚佢會做傻事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好啊！唔好為啲咁嘅男人）<br />\n<br />\n正當BOYZ上年演唱會可以重領風騷，仲以為Steven大個仔生生性性，難得20年之後終於可以因為網民集氣上紅館舞台，點知埋門一腳衰咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔通係因為攞咗許志安過紅館檔期，Steven都變埋一個壞咗嘅人？唔知最後搞唔搞得成呢？小賓女今次又因為隊友搞彎自己嘅事業啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14XQorZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14XQorZ.png&h=6022eb0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VrWE1dF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVrWE1dF.png&h=abf201c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5kaN960.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5kaN960.png&h=95a5a2bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https